'''Supreme Prophet''' of the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] was the title of the highest ranking member of the [[Dark Force]] clergy.

==History==
The founder of the religion, [[Darth Millennial]], bestowed this title upon himself. Under the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], an alternate title was '''Supreme Prophet of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]'''. This title was bestowed upon [[Kadann]] by [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Galactic Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], and later usurped by the [[Rajah Ubooki|pseudo-Kadann]].

